## üè∞ Tower System (5 Types)

### Core Towers
**Cannon Tower** (25 gold)
- Damage: 25, Range: 80px, Fire Rate: 1.5/sec
- Special: Splash damage (20px radius)
- Role: Area damage, crowd control

**Machine Gun Tower** (40 gold)
- Damage: 8, Range: 60px, Fire Rate: 5/sec  
- Special: High accuracy, rapid fire
- Role: Anti-swarm, consistent DPS

**Missile Tower** (60 gold)
- Damage: 40, Range: 100px, Fire Rate: 0.8/sec
- Special: Homing missiles, anti-air
- Role: High damage, flying units

### Advanced Towers
**Laser Tower** (80 gold)
- Damage: 15, Range: 70px, Fire Rate: 10/sec
- Special: Piercing projectiles hit multiple enemies
- Role: Line damage, armor penetration

**Freeze Tower** (50 gold)
- Damage: 12, Range: 90px, Fire Rate: 2.0/sec
- Special: Freeze effect (3s duration, 50% slow, 25px splash)
- Role: Crowd control, enemy manipulation

### Upgrade System
- **3 upgrade levels** per tower
- **Progressive costs**: [25, 45, 70] gold for Freeze Tower
- **Stat scaling**: Damage, range, and fire rate improvements
- **Special enhancement**: Increased effect radius and duration

## üëæ Enemy System (12 Types)

### Basic Enemies
- **Basic Infantry**: 50 HP, 30 speed, 5 gold
- **Fast Scout**: 25 HP, 60 speed, 8 gold  
- **Heavy Tank**: 150 HP, 15 speed, 15 gold
- **Flying Unit**: 40 HP, 40 speed, 12 gold (immune to splash)

### Advanced Enemies
- **Armored Enemy**: 80 HP, 25 speed, 10 gold (5 armor)
- **Boss Enemy**: 300 HP, 20 speed, 25 gold (10 armor, 2 HP/sec regen)
- **Elite Enemy**: 60 HP, 45 speed, 15 gold (flying, fast)
- **Swarm Enemy**: 15 HP, 50 speed, 3 gold (small, numerous)

### Level 5 Enemies
- **Stealth Enemy**: 45 HP, 35 speed, 12 gold (periodic invisibility)
- **Berserker Enemy**: 70 HP, 40 speed, 18 gold (speed boost when damaged)
- **Titan Enemy**: 500 HP, 10 speed, 50 gold (massive, heavy armor)
- **Phantom Enemy**: 30 HP, 50 speed, 20 gold (teleportation ability)

## üó∫Ô∏è Level System (5 Levels)

### Level 1: "Green Valley" (Tutorial)
- **Difficulty**: Beginner
- **Path**: Simple straight path
- **Waves**: 10 waves, basic enemy introduction
- **Focus**: Learning tower placement and basics

### Level 2: "Mountain Pass" (Intermediate)  
- **Difficulty**: Moderate
- **Path**: Zigzag mountain terrain
- **Waves**: 10 waves, armored enemies introduced
- **Focus**: Strategic positioning

### Level 3: "Desert Canyon" (Advanced)
- **Difficulty**: Hard
- **Path**: Serpentine canyon with tight curves
- **Waves**: 10 waves, boss enemies and elite units
- **Focus**: Advanced tactics and timing

### Level 4: "Volcanic Crater" (Expert)
- **Difficulty**: Very Hard
- **Path**: Complex volcanic terrain with multiple branches
- **Waves**: 10 waves, all enemy types with heavy armor
- **Focus**: Mastery of all tower combinations

### Level 5: "Frozen Wasteland" (Legendary)
- **Difficulty**: Legendary
- **Path**: 67-waypoint full circle with multiple chokepoints
- **Waves**: 10 escalating waves ending with 400+ enemies
- **Focus**: Ultimate challenge requiring freeze tower mastery

