### Enhanced Controls Summary
**Keyboard:**
- WASD/Arrows: Camera panning
- 1-5: Tower selection (Cannon, Machine Gun, Missile, Laser, Freeze)
- N: Skip to next wave
- P: Pause/unpause  
- R: Restart
- 1-5 (Menu): Level selection

**Mouse:**
- Left Click: Place tower (in game area) or click UI buttons
- "Start Next Wave" button: Skip waiting between waves
- Tower selection buttons: Visual tower picker with sprites
- Tower clicking: Upgrade existing towers

**UI Features:**
- Visual countdown timer with color warnings
- Interactive skip wave button
- Real-time force timer display
- 5-tower selection panel with proper spacing
- Upgrade cost and stat display

